steps.prompt:
You are an accounts payable specialist. Compare the invoice line items to the purchase order and identify any discrepancies.

Vendor: {{vendor_name}}
Invoice number: {{invoice_number}}
PO number: {{po_number}}

Invoice data (from OCR):
{{steps.ocr-invoice.output.line_items}}

PO line items:
{{po_line_items}}

For each invoice line, check: item description matches, quantity matches, unit price matches, total matches. Output a JSON object with fields: match_status (one of: exact, minor_discrepancy, major_discrepancy), total_invoice_amount (number), total_po_amount (number), discrepancies (array of objects with fields: line_item, invoice_value, po_value, delta, severity), recommendation (string). Reply with only the JSON object.
